So you won't get questions on the exam.

33
00:02:22,040 --> 00:02:26,240
You might be asked what's at ring zero to which you will answer the system kernel.

34
00:02:26,240 --> 00:02:30,320
And you might get questions about ring three, because ring three is always where your

35
00:02:30,320 --> 00:02:32,800
user programs run.

