00:05:01,320 --> 00:05:05,520
And you probably notice that every so often you get a little nudge from Apple saying,

75
00:05:05,520 --> 00:05:07,000
hey, you need to update your device.

76
00:05:07,000 --> 00:05:12,240
Hey, hey, and what you're going to go and do is you're going to go into system settings

77
00:05:12,240 --> 00:05:14,920
and you're going to say, update my device.

78
00:05:14,920 --> 00:05:17,560
And when you've done this, you probably notice that when you say, you know,

