just downloaded actually came from Apple because if you're downloading an update to your

90
00:05:52,520 --> 00:05:55,440
phone that's going to make a whole bunch of changes to your operating system, you want

91
00:05:55,440 --> 00:05:58,000
to make darn sure that actually came from a trusted source.

92
