98
00:06:19,080 --> 00:06:24,800
You want to make sure that that whole software update is complete, has integrity.

99
00:06:24,800 --> 00:06:29,840
And so that's the two major pieces of functionality that code signing provides.

100
00:06:29,840 --> 00:06:33,360
It allows you to know where a software update came from.

101
00:06:33,360 --> 00:06:38,480
